        It all started with recirculation. Our analytics were telling us that a majority of the traffic was coming in straight to a project page and bouncing. We started by investigating experience patterns that would frame an individual page as part of a larger lexicon of creativity on the site, and demonstrate the breadth of projects currently seeking funding. This lead us to “the stream.”
