        Ultimately, due to a change in leadership and concerns about feasibility and strategy, the bulk of this project was shelved. We made an exorcize of pulling out viable concepts and scoping them as projects on the roadmaps of various focus teams, but shifting priorities left those mostly unrealized as well. In the end, we learned a lot about conceptualizing the future of a product, but not a lot about actually getting us there.
